{"tid":1266874,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】熱爆全球　小球迷鬧爆：「曼聯嘅在座各位都係垃圾」","createTime":"2019-06-29T16:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T09:50:02.000Z","uid":268711,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a54d6e50f45b958566268f2db919db35af69d14c","tid":1266874,"uid":268711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:07:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0-8slTAp84w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0-8slTAp84w&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJozDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=fa8c319d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0-8slTAp84w</a><br />\n<br />\n自從費格遜退休之後，曼聯好似冇咗靈魂，表現長期浮浮沉沉，令人失望，連小朋友都睇唔過眼。<br />\n<br />\n近日有一段訪問熱爆全球，1位曼聯小球迷接受電視台訪問時，直斥現時所有曼聯球員都係垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n當時呢位小紅魔球迷正參與足球訓練，其後有記者訪問佢，雙方對答內容如下：<br />\n<br />\n記者：「你將來有冇打算成為1位球員?」<br />\n<br />\n小球迷：「有，希望得啦。」<br />\n<br />\n記者：「你最鍾意邊支球隊?」<br />\n<br />\n小球迷：「曼聯。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">記者：「咁你最鍾意邊位曼聯球員？」<br />\n<br />\n小球迷：「一個都冇，佢哋全部都係垃圾。」</span><br />\n<br />\n記者即時忍唔住大笑：「咁蘇斯克查呢？你應該喜歡佢啦？」<br />\n<br />\n小球迷：「係，佢係一位傳奇。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然訪問只有短短幾十秒，但已經道出所有曼聯球迷嘅心聲，難怪呢段片立即喺網上瘋傳，仲成為英國各大傳媒報道焦點。曼聯球員聽完，真係要好好反省一下。"},{"pid":"95e1baf50bb2124d216674ca1113016e517cfabd","tid":1266874,"uid":133424,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:19:26.000Z","msg":"我係話在座嘅各位都係垃圾"},{"pid":"3ab2a891573f1755b1c3e78ffae39d94fba7c228","tid":1266874,"uid":67225,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T01:56:05.000Z","msg":"會反省就唔僲話水0.012%啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e22865d1dc202cdf75b1dc8aa92026e854eaed","tid":1266874,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T01:56:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會反省就唔會話0.012%啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/